Cyber Claw:




Cyber saw the big raptor slash at her, and she ducked. She leaped back and 
snapped twice into the air, but after that insticts kicked in. Fight back or 
die.

She screeched loudly and transformed to her robot mode. Her long shoulder 
spikes protruded out, and her eyes were wild with her stony face. She leaped 
into the air, activating her flight mode. She shot up a few feet and kicked 
her foot out at Dinobot. She leaped back down, landing by the door where 
Tavatron was. She have her no eye contact, just shouldered her hashly out of 
the way.

After that, she stood her ground, with her feet spread in a steady position.

"Open this door!" she commanded in her harsh, hissing voice that was her 
own. "Open this door, slag you!"
